## News Aggregator API

## Description:-
A RESTful News Aggregator API built with Node.js and Express.js that allows users to register, authenticate using JWT, manage their news preferences, and fetch personalized news articles.

## WorkFlow of Application:-
Client
    │
    ▼
Login
    │
    ▼
JWT Generated
    │
    ▼
Authorization: Bearer <token>/Cookier - Works on both scenarios
    │
    ▼
Authentication Middleware
    │
    ▼
User Preferences
    │
    ▼
External News API
    │
    ▼
Personalized News Response


## Installation

1. Clone the repository

git clone <repository-url>

2. Install dependencies

npm install

3. Create a .env file

PORT=3000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
API_KEY=your_news_api_key

4. Start the server

npm run dev